Age and Gender

.. _eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jantotal_nr_t:

Population on 1 January - Total, Total
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------





Population on 1 January - Total, Total





Measure "Population on 1 January - Total, Total"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jantotal_nr_t'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - Total, Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jantotal_nr_t'
        );

   </tr>

.. _eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany1_nr_t:

Population on 1 January - 1 year, Total
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^





Population on 1 January - 1 year, Total





Measure "Population on 1 January - 1 year, Total"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany1_nr_t'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 1 year, Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany1_nr_t'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 1 year, Total" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany1_nr_t',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 1 year, Total" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany1_nr_t',
        'denominator'
      );

Measure "Population on 1 January - 9 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany9_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 9 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany9_nr_f'
        );

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany9_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 44 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 44 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany44_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 44 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany44_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 44 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany44_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 44 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany44_nr_f',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 51 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 51 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany51_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 51 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany51_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 51 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany51_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 51 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany51_nr_f',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 58 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 58 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany58_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 58 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany58_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 58 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany58_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 58 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany58_nr_f',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 65 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 65 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany65_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 65 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany65_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 65 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany65_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 65 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany65_nr_f',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 72 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 72 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany72_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 72 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany72_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 72 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany72_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 72 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany72_nr_f',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 79 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 79 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany79_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 79 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany79_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 79 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany79_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 79 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany79_nr_f',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 86 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 86 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany86_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 86 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany86_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 86 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany86_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 86 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =

        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany86_nr_f',

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 93 years, Females





Measure "Population on 1 January - 93 years, Females"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany93_nr_f'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 93 years, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany93_nr_f'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 93 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany93_nr_f',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 93 years, Females" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Females" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany93_nr_f',

      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 25 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 25 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany25_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 25 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany25_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 25 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany25_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 25 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany25_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 32 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 32 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany32_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 32 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany32_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 32 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany32_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 32 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany32_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 39 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 39 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany39_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 39 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany39_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 39 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany39_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 39 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany39_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 46 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 46 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany46_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 46 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany46_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 46 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany46_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 46 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany46_nr_m',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 53 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 53 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany53_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 53 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany53_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 53 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany53_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 53 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany53_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 60 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 60 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany60_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 60 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany60_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 60 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany60_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 60 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany60_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 67 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 67 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany67_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 67 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany67_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 67 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany67_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 67 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany67_nr_m',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 74 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 74 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany74_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 74 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany74_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 74 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany74_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 74 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany74_nr_m',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 81 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 81 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany81_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 81 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany81_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 81 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany81_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 81 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany81_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 88 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 88 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany88_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 88 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany88_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 88 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany88_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 88 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany88_nr_m',
        'denominator'

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - 95 years, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - 95 years, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany95_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - 95 years, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany95_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - 95 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany95_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - 95 years, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_jany95_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""





Population on 1 January - Unknown, Males





Measure "Population on 1 January - Unknown, Males"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_janunk_nr_m'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - Unknown, Males" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_janunk_nr_m'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - Unknown, Males" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Males" at one point:

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_d2_janunk_nr_m',
        'denominator'
      );

Population on 1 January - From 65 to 69 years, Total





Measure "Population on 1 January - From 65 to 69 years, Total"  density per sq. kilometer  for one point:


.. code-block:: postgresql





  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_pjangroupy65_69_nr_t'
      );





Measure "Population on 1 January - From 65 to 69 years, Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

    UPDATE {table_name}
      SET {new_numeric_column} =
        OBS_GetMeasure(
          ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
          'eu.eurostat.demo_r_pjangroupy65_69_nr_t'
        );






Measure "Population on 1 January - From 65 to 69 years, Total" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Total" at one point:

.. code-block:: postgresql

  UPDATE {table_name}
    SET {new_numeric_column} =
      OBS_GetMeasure(
        CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945),
        'eu.eurostat.demo_r_pjangroupy65_69_nr_t',
        'denominator'
      );


Measure "Population on 1 January - From 65 to 69 years, Total" percent of "Population on 1 January - Total, Total" within an area:

.. code-block:: postgresql

      OBS_GetMeasure(
        ST_Buffer(CDB_LatLng(52.5220703614, 13.4060668945), 0.01),
